01:18:46.527 --> 01:18:49.298
Still you are working?

01:18:54.510 --> 01:18:57.272
As a what?

01:19:05.636 --> 01:19:07.216
Oh, Babu, yes.

01:19:07.241 --> 01:19:10.147
Worked in India also, is it?

01:19:10.889 --> 01:19:14.040
How do you know the word Babu?

01:19:14.770 --> 01:19:18.125
I know, but how do you know?

01:19:20.626 --> 01:19:23.885
Oh, I see, that's good.

01:19:24.587 --> 01:19:26.733
Haan?

01:19:28.099 --> 01:19:28.579
Haan?

01:19:28.604 --> 01:19:29.327
Hard.

01:19:29.352 --> 01:19:30.747
Left, left side you raise.

01:19:30.772 --> 01:19:31.507
Yes.

01:19:31.532 --> 01:19:33.734
You work very hard?

01:19:35.957 --> 01:19:36.550
All right.

01:19:36.575 --> 01:19:37.777
Just raise his left.

01:19:37.802 --> 01:19:40.330
But you have worked very hard.

01:19:47.503 --> 01:19:50.187
Regis, do you mind seeing this gentleman has

01:19:50.212 --> 01:19:51.692
got it or not?

01:19:51.717 --> 01:19:53.823
There's somebody here.

01:19:54.090 --> 01:19:56.578
Has she got it?

01:19:58.207 --> 01:19:59.629
What happened to that?